ibute-value">en</a>" <span class="attribute-name">xml:lang</span>="<a class="attribute-value">en</a>"&gt;\r\n<span id="line223"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">https://twitter.com/RiotKatana</a>"&gt;@RiotKatana&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/lolesports">https://twitter.com/lolesports</a>"&gt;@lolesports&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan">https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan</a>"&gt;@ZionSpartan&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; when it comes to lategame, make sure you save your E to protect yourself from the ADC rather than stun&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line224"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;— Diego Ruiz (@CrsQuas) &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/CrsQuas/status/507390989104054272">https://twitter.com/CrsQuas/status/507390989104054272</a>"&gt;September 4, 2014&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">blockquote</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line225"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">script</span> <span class="attribute-name">async</span>="" <span class="attribute-name">src</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js">//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js</a>" <span class="attribute-name">charset</span>="<a class="attribute-value">utf-8</a>"&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">script</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">center</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line226"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;Essentially the opposite of Zion''s last tip, Quas''s recommendation is for the more even-keeled lover of Jax. While his E is a great way to initiate a teamfight, it also means that you''ll be completely vulnerable after you use it. If you don''t have a ton of armor, saving the invulnerability can be a safer way to play it...but where''s the fun in that?&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line227"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">h3</span>&gt;Community Tips&lt;/<span class="end-tag">h3</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line228"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">center</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">br</span> /&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">blockquote</span> <span class="attribute-name">class</span>="<a class="attribute-value">twitter-tweet</a>" <span class="attribute-name">data-conversation</span>="<a class="attribute-value">none</a>" <span class="attribute-name">lang</span>="<a class="attribute-value">en</a>" <span class="attribute-name">xml:lang</span>="<a class="attribute-value">en</a>"&gt;\r\n<span id="line229"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">https://twitter.com/RiotKatana</a>"&gt;@RiotKatana&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/lolesports">https://twitter.com/lolesports</a>"&gt;@lolesports&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan">https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan</a>"&gt;@ZionSpartan&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/CrsQuas">https://twitter.com/CrsQuas</a>"&gt;@CrsQuas&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt; the W is an auto attack reset. so you should use it immediately after an autoattack&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line230"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;— Cloudwalker/Angwar (@MalteMittelhaus) &lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:https://twitter.com/MalteMittelhaus/status/507169816218984448">https://twitter.com/MalteMittelhaus/status/507169816218984448</a>"&gt;September 3, 2014&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">blockquote</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line231"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">script</span> <span class="attribute-name">async</span>="" <span class="attribute-name">src</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js">//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js</a>" <span class="attribute-name">charset</span>="<a class="attribute-value">utf-8</a>"&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">script</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">center</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line232"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;Auto attack resets are an important part of being able to trade effectively. The extra burst of damage can easily be the difference between life and death, especially in the lonely island of top lane. Use your W immediately after auto attacking for a surprising burst of damage. &lt;/<span class="end-tag">p</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line233"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">p</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">strong</span>&gt;Vote for next week''s Pro Tip to help