olesports.com/articles/lcs-pro-tips-Elise">/articles/lcs-pro-tips-Elise</a>"&gt;LCS Pro Tips: Elise&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">li</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line238"></span>&lt;<span class="start-tag">li</span>&gt;&lt;<span class="start-tag">a</span> <span class="attribute-name">href</span>="<a class="attribute-value" href="view-source:http://na.lolesports.com/articles/lcs-pro-tips-renekton-0">/articles/lcs-pro-tips-renekton-0</a>"&gt;LCS Pro Tips: Renekton&lt;/<span class="end-tag">a</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">li</span>&gt;\r\n<span id="line239"></span>&lt;/<span class="end-tag">ul</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">div</span>&gt;&lt;/<span class="end-tag">div</span>&gt;\r\n</pre>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Jax', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 15:39:24', '2014-09-12 15:39:24', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=42', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(43, 1, '2014-09-12 15:43:38', '2014-09-12 15:43:38', '<h3>1. ZionSpartan - 72.8% (843 Votes)</h3>\n<a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/811aea3286.jpg?itok=SbVzO5s1"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/811aea3286.jpg?itok=SbVzO5s1" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>\n\n<strong>LCS Jax Stats:</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>: 6</li>\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 4</li>\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 66.7%</li>\n	<li><em>Average KDA:</em> 2.7</li>\n</ul>\n<pre id="line1"></pre>\n<center>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas">@CrsQuas</a> When it comes to splitpushing, never underestimate your ability to pressure the turret while ahead 1/2\n\n— Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507393034355765248">September 4, 2014</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n&nbsp;\n</center><center>\n\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\n<a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas">@CrsQuas</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> You can always go for potshots on towers with jax when you are ahead, especially with a trinity force! :)\n\n— Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507393189377245184">September 4, 2014</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</center>Today we learned that if you ask ZionSpartan about one of his favorite champions, you get three tips for the price of one. Jax is a notoriously strong split pusher thanks to some help from a stacking attack speed passive. Everyone knows that turrets are week to lamp posts. Zion is suggesting that if you''ve got a lot of damage and are ahead in lane, don''t be afraid to poke the tower.\n\n<center>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas">@CrsQuas</a> Also, never underestimate the ability to initiate a teamfight by flash counterstriking into the enemy team!\n\n— Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507395748666015745">September 4, 2014</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</center>And there''s the tip we really wanted. This is the Jax player dream: Flash-Leap Striking onto the enemy ADC and getting off that three man stun while your team (hopefully) follows up behind you. Bear in mind that you <em>have to</em> have good communication with your team or you''ll be a lonely Jax behind enemy lines. If you''re all on the same page, though, this is a really great initiate especially if your team can pile on the cc.\n<h3>2. Quas - 12.3% (142 Votes)</h3>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Jax', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '41-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 15:43:38', '2014-09-12 15:43:38', '', 41, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=43', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
