(48, 1, '2014-09-12 15:52:15', '2014-09-12 15:52:15', '<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n<h3>1. Meteos- 57.9% (963 Votos)</h3>\r\n<a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>LCS Elise Estadisticas:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Jugados</em>: 5</li>\r\n	<li><em>Games Ganados</em>: 3</li>\r\n	<li><em>Ratio</em>: 60%</li>\r\n	<li><em> KDA:</em> 6.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> apply red buff with an auto attack before going for a stun to make it easier to hit\r\n\r\n— Will Hartman (@meteoslol) <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol/statuses/504463837987614720">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Si bien hay</span> <span class="hps">campeones</span> <span class="hps">que</span> <span class="hps">pueden tener éxito</span> <span class="hps">sin ellos</span>, <span class="hps">una especie de</span> <span class="hps">brecha de</span> <span class="hps">cerca</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">hace que</span> <span class="hps">la presión</span> <span class="hps">del juego</span> <span class="hps">temprano y</span> <span class="hps">ganks</span> <span class="hps">mucho más fácil</span>. <span class="hps">Disparos</span> <span class="hps">de habilidad</span> <span class="hps">que falte en un</span> <span class="hps">ataque en masa</span> <span class="hps">pueden</span> <span class="hps">terminar perdiendo</span> <span class="hps">un valioso tiempo de</span> <span class="hps">selva</span> <span class="hps">claro.</span> <span class="hps">Capullo</span> <span class="hps">de Elise</span> <span class="hps">puede ser muy</span> <span class="hps">difícil de golpear</span> <span class="hps">si el</span> <span class="hps">compañero de equipo</span> <span class="hps">que estés</span> <span class="hps">ganking</span> <span class="hps">para</span> <span class="hps">no tiene</span> <span class="hps">algún tipo de</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">fiable</span>, <span class="hps">así que trate de</span> <span class="hps">ataque</span> <span class="hps">automático con</span> <span class="hps">piel de ante</span> <span class="hps">de color rojo</span> <span class="hps">para que sea un</span> <span class="hps">poco más fácil</span> <span class="hps">para usted</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Shook - 15.8% (262 Votos)</h3>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>   <strong>LCS Elise Estadisticas:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Jugados</em>:9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Ganados</em>: 7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ratio</em>: 77.8%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>KDA</em>: 2.9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<center></center>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> When ganking just apply redbuff and use your damaging abbilities, hold on to your cocoon until they flash. — Shook (@ShookLoL) <a href="https://twitter.com/ShookLoL/statuses/504778852149649408">August 27, 2014</a>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div id="gt-res-content" class="almost_half_cell">\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Shook</span> <span class="hps">refuerza</span> <span class="hps">lo</span> <span class="hps">Meteos</span> <span class="hps">nos dijo</span>, <span class="hps">porque</span> <span class="hps">incluso los profesionales</span> <span class="hps">saben que es</span> <span class="hps">fácil pasar por alto</span> <span class="hps">un capullo</span>. <span class="hps">La</span> <span class="hps">piel de ante</span> <span class="hps">rojo</span> <span class="hps">lento</span> <span class="hps">también</span> <span class="hps">hará que sea</span> <span class="hps">más fácil para sus</span> <span class="hps">Laners</span> <span class="hps">para golpear a</span> <span class="hps">cualquier</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">​​que tienen,</span> <span class="hps">como un gancho</span> <span class="hps">Thresh</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">una burbuja de</span> <span class="hps">Nami</span><span>.</span></span></div>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Tips de la comunidad</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol">@meteoslol</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> cocoon flash is a nice way to hit an unexpected stun. channel your cocoon and then cancel the animation with flash\r\n\r\n— I Will Dominate (@CrsDominate) <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate/statuses/504469712701779968">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>  <span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Había un poco de</span> <span class="hps">debate</span> <span class="hps">en Twitter</span> <span class="hps">en torno a</span> <span class="hps">éste</span>, así que <span class="hps">probé</span> <span class="hps">yo mismo</span> <span class="hps">sólo para estar seguro</span> <span class="hps">(no es que</span> <span class="hps">no confíe en ti</span>, <span class="hps">Dom)</span>. <span class="hps">Uso del flash</span> <span class="hps">inmediatamente</span> <span class="hps">después de la fundición</span> <span class="hps">capullo</span> <span class="hps">cancela</span> <span class="hps">la animación</span> <span class="hps">canalización</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">arroja</span> <span class="hps">el capullo</span> <span class="hps">al instante</span> <span class="hps">de la</span> <span class="hps">ubicación final</span> <span class="hps">del</span> <span class="hps">flash</span>. <span class="hps">Esto significa</span> <span class="hps">menos tiempo</span> <span class="hps">al enemigo para</span> <span class="hps">reaccionar y</span> <span class="hps">una mayor probabilidad de</span> <span class="hps">golpear</span><span>.</span></span>\r\n<center></center>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> Starting off tower dives is great on Elise. She can tank 2-3 shots and then repel in order to reset tower Aggro. — TomsGG (@SomePlatDude) <a href="https://twitter.com/SomePlatDude/statuses/504877341772742656">August 28, 2014</a>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Mientras</span> <span class="hps">torretas</span> <span class="hps">de buceo</span> <span class="hps">puede ser peligroso</span>, especialmente <span class="hps">al principio del juego</span>, es <span class="hps">también</span> <span class="hps">una gran manera de</span> <span class="hps">bola de nieve</span> <span class="hps">sus</span> <span class="hps">carriles</span>. <span class="hps">Como</span> <span class="hps">SomePlatDude</span> <span class="hps">señala</span>, <span class="hps">Elise</span> <span class="hps">es muy bueno para</span> <span class="hps">iniciar</span> <span class="hps">ya que ella</span> <span class="hps">lo</span> <span class="hps">puede</span> <span class="hps">conseguir fácilmente</span> <span class="hps">fuera de rango</span> <span class="hps">aggro</span> <span class="hps">torre.</span></span>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate">@CrsDominate</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol">@meteoslol</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> Using your spider form Q to close in distance when chasing through a creep wave. Small but noticable\r\n\r\n— Ram Djemal (@BrokenshardEUW) <a href="https://twitter.com/BrokenshardEUW/statuses/504472221294014464">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Aunque estoy</span> <span class="hps">seguro de que ninguno</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">nosotros ha</span> <span class="hps">perdido</span> <span class="hps">aturdimiento</span> <span class="hps">de Elise</span>, <span class="hps">Brokenshard</span> <span class="hps">ofrece</span> <span class="hps">un gran consejo</span> <span class="hps">para atacar a los</span> <span class="hps">enemigos</span>. <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps">usted tiene</span> <span class="hps">suficientes</span> <span class="hps">dedos rápidos</span>, <span class="hps">también puede utilizar</span> <span class="hps">este truco</span> <span class="hps">como una manera de</span> <span class="hps">ponerse en posición</span> <span class="hps">para</span> <span class="hps">una mejor oportunidad de</span> <span class="hps">conseguir el</span> <span class="hps">aturdimiento</span> <span class="hps">en el primer lugar</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Elise', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'lcs-pro-tips-elise', '', '', '2014-09-15 11:08:22', '2014-09-15 11:08:22', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=48', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(49, 1, '2014-09-12 15:52:15', '2014-09-12 15:52:15', '<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n<h3>1. Meteos- 57.9% (963 Votes)</h3>\r\n<a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>LCS Elise Stats:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>: 5</li>\r\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 3</li>\r\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 60%</li>\r\n	<li><em>Average KDA:</em> 6.1</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> apply red buff with an auto attack before going for a stun to make it easier to hit\r\n\r\n— Will Hartman (@meteoslol) <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol/statuses/504463837987614720">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>  While there are champions that can be successful without them, some kind of gap close or cc makes early game pressure and ganks much easier. Missing skill shots on a gank can end up wasting valuable jungle clearing time. Elise''s cocoon can be very difficult to hit if the teammate you''re ganking for doesn''t have some kind of reliable cc, so try to auto attack with red buff to make it a bit easier for yourself.   \r\n\r\n<h3>2. Shook - 15.8% (262 Votes)</h3>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>   <strong>LCS Elise Stats:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>:9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 77.8%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Average KDA</em>: 2.9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<center></center>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> When ganking just apply redbuff and use your damaging abbilities, hold on to your cocoon until they flash. — Shook (@ShookLoL) <a href="https://twitter.com/ShookLoL/statuses/504778852149649408">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nShook reinforces what Meteos told us, because even the pros know that it''s easy to miss a cocoon. The red buff slow will also make it easier for your laners to hit any cc they have, like a Thresh hook or a Nami bubble.\r\n<h3>Community Tips</h3>\r\nThis week, we got some bonus tips from a few more pro players and some more great advice from members of the community!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol">@meteoslol</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> cocoon flash is a nice way to hit an unexpected stun. channel your cocoon and then cancel the animation with flash\r\n\r\n— I Will Dominate (@CrsDominate) <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate/statuses/504469712701779968">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>  There was a little debate on Twitter around this one so I tested this myself just to be sure (not that I don''t trust you, Dom). Using Flash immediately after casting cocoon cancels the channeling animation and casts the cocoon instantly from the final location of the Flash. This means less time for the enemy to react and a higher chance of hitting them.  \r\n<center></center>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> Starting off tower dives is great on Elise. She can tank 2-3 shots and then repel in order to reset tower Aggro. — TomsGG (@SomePlatDude) <a href="https://twitter.com/SomePlatDude/statuses/504877341772742656">August 28, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhile diving turrets can be dangerous, especially in the early game, it’s also a great way to snowball your lanes. As SomePlatDude points out, Elise is great at initiating since she can so easily get out of tower aggro range.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate">@CrsDominate</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol">@meteoslol</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> Using your spider form Q to close in distance when chasing through a creep wave. Small but noticable\r\n\r\n— Ram Djemal (@BrokenshardEUW) <a href="https://twitter.com/BrokenshardEUW/statuses/504472221294014464">August 27, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nEven though I''m sure none of us have <em>ever</em> missed Elise''s stun, Brokenshard offers a great tip for chasing down enemies. If you''ve got fast enough fingers, you can also use this tip as a way to get in position for a better chance at landing the stun in the first place.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Elise', '', 'inherit', 