r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> you can E an enemy minion to give your Glitterlance longer range.\r\n\r\n— Christopher S Garcia (@ChrisGarcia320) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisGarcia320/statuses/496779770550448129">August 5, 2014</a>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</center>Extending the range of your Glitterlance means that you can harass from a much safer distance, making this a great tip.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Lulu', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 16:29:38', '2014-09-12 16:29:38', '', 70, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=71', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(72, 1, '2014-09-12 16:31:18', '2014-09-12 16:31:18', '<img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Lulu_OriginalSkin.jpg?itok=44qGabX_" alt="" width="700" height="315" />\r\n<h1><strong><em>Click on image</em></strong></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div class="field-content"></div>\r\n<div class="field-content">We asked you to choose your favorite Lulu players and the results are in! Check out their best tips for playing him.</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Lulu', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '69-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 16:31:18', '2014-09-12 16:31:18', '', 69, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=72', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(73, 1, '2014-09-12 16:31:21', '2014-09-12 16:31:21', '<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n\r\nSupport? Says who? Lulu may not have been designed for mid or top lane, but she has certainly found her niche there. Upon release, Lulu jumped around the map more than almost any other champion, with players taking her to almost every lane. Who can forget the days of on hit attack speed Lulu in the top lane?\r\n\r\nThese days, she still doesn''t see much play as a support as intended, but she makes for some pretty whimsical teamfights just the same. More recently, she has even become a priority pick for some players due to her ability to bully melee champions and deliver tons of utility in the mid to late game.\r\n\r\nWe asked you for your favorite LCS Lulu players and we''ve tallied the votes! Fnatic''s sOAZ took a big lead due to some of his dominating performances, followed by TSM''s Dyrus and LMQ''s Ackerman.\r\n<h3>1. sOAZ- 36.7% (1,074 Votes)</h3>\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/3a0fe718bf_0.jpg?itok=8At--dR3" alt="" width="700" height="315" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>LCS Lulu Stats:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>: 6</li>\r\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 5</li>\r\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 83.3%</li>\r\n	<li><em>Average KDA</em>: 9.5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> buy 3 doran rings and enjoy. always save your ulti for the strongest member unless you have a really good engage and go hamm !\r\n\r\n— Paul Boyer (@FnaticsOAZ) <a href="https://twitter.com/FnaticsOAZ/statuses/496733718682566656">August 5, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n Sometimes it''s hard to avoid the urge to ult yourself unless you''re like me (chronic support syndrome). sOAZ''s tip is a great reminder that to maximize Lulu''s utility, one of her most valuable attributes, you should ult your most powerful teammate. He also gives a bold tip on how to start off your item build with more rings than a middle aged divorcée.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h3>2. Dyrus - 28.9% (846 Votes)</h3>\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/6c96be4890.jpg?itok=STmYsVKz" alt="" width="700" height="315" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>LCS Lulu Stats:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>:5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 40%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Average KDA</em>: 2.2</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<center></center>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> play safe vs maokai eve, respect your opponents, and expect them to punish you for bad play\r\n\r\n— Marcus (@LoLDyrus) <a href="https://twitter.com/LoLDyrus/statuses/496729224674570240">August 5, 2014</a>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> and I guess lulu specific, learn the mechanics of when to push and when to harass. press R and use W to hex not speed in fights\r\n\r\n— Marcus (@LoLDyrus) <a href="https://twitter.com/LoLDyrus/statuses/496729638182588417">August 5, 2014</a></blockquote>\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n \r\n \r\n Dyrus'' tips are mostly centered around the idea that as a top laner, Lulu is a pretty fragile pick. She''s great at harassing from afar, forcing enemy champions away from the minion wave, and pushing, but you also need to be very careful not to get caught out before level 6. Respecting your lane opponent and junglers with a lot of crowd control is extremely important.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h3>3. Ackerman - 13.5% (396 Votes)</h3>\r\n\r\n<img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/0038b1b8c2.jpg?itok=PmtjmQTl" alt="" width="700" height="315" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nI couldn''t catch up with Ackerman on Twitter, but we still got his pro tip!\r\n\r\n"Take advantage of Lulu''s passive, using her auto attack to constantly harass your opponent in the lane. As for Lulu''s build, cooldown reduction is crucial for her, I recommend Athene''s Unholy Grail, Ionian Boots of Lucidity, Lich Bane, Rabbadon''s Deathcap, Zhonya''s Hourglass, and Void Staff."\r\n\r\nLulu''s passive does a lot more damage than many players expect. As I mentioned at the start of the article, attack speed and on hit effects used to be very popular on Lulu because of her ability to do bonus magic damage with each auto. Ackerman''s tip is a great way to bully your lane opponent, especially if they are a melee champion.\r\n\r\n<strong>LCS Lulu Stats:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Played</em>: 7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Games Won</em>: 5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Win Rate</em>: 71.4%</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Average KDA:</em> 4.5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<h3>Community Tip</h3>\r\n\r\nChoosing a tip this week was especially hard because there were great ones for top, mid, and support. In the end I went with one that could help you in any role.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<center></center>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana">@RiotKatana</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports">@lolesports</a> you can E an enemy minion to give your Glitterlance longer range.\r\n\r\n— Christopher S Garcia (@ChrisGarcia320) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisGarcia320/statuses/496779770550448129">August 5, 2014</a>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nExtending the range of your Glitterlance means that you can harass from a much safer distance, making this a great tip.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Lulu', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '70-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 16:31:21', '2014-09-12 16:31:21', '', 70, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=73', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(74, 1, '2014-09-12 17:27:48', '2014-09-12 17:27:48', '<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=75"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/SG_A1920x1080.jpg?itok=JQOIKYCS" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></a>\r\n<h1><strong><em>Click en la imagen\r\n</em></strong></h1>\r\nToda la informacion sobre los teams en el grupo A!', 'Breaking down Group A', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'breaking-down-group-a', '', '', '2014-09-15 11:09:06', '2014-09-15 11:09:06', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=74', 0, 'post', '', 0);
