pan> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Samsung</span> <span class="hps">Galaxy</span> <span class="hps">White</span> <span class="hps">dependen</span> <span class="hps">en gran medida de</span> <span class="hps">sus</span> <span class="hps">Junglers</span>, <span class="hps">y ambos</span> <span class="hps">son conocidos por</span> <span class="hps">una bola de nieve</span> <span class="hps">juegos</span> <span class="hps">a su favor</span>. <span class="hps">Ellos</span> <span class="hps">tienden a</span> <span class="hps">hacerlo</span> <span class="hps">de diferentes maneras</span>, <span class="hps">sin embargo, con</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">forzar</span> <span class="hps">teamfights</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">las nubes</span> <span class="hps">números</span> <span class="hps">de interrupción,</span> <span class="hps">y blanco</span> <span class="hps">tiende</span> <span class="hps">a centrarse más en</span> <span class="hps">el control</span> <span class="hps">objetivo</span>. <span class="hps">Los dos</span> <span class="hps">ejemplifican</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">estilo de juego</span> <span class="hps">de sus respectivas</span> <span class="hps">regiones</span> <span class="hps">son conocidos por</span>, <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">parecen bastante</span> <span class="hps">imparable</span> <span class="hps">cuando están en</span> <span class="hps">su juego</span>.</span></div>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"></div>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Es decir,</span> <span class="hps">a menos</span> <span class="hps">AHQ</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Dark Passage</span> <span class="hps">figura</span> <span class="hps">una manera de</span> <span class="hps">contener</span> <span class="hps">la presión</span> <span clas