/span> <span class="hps">posicionamiento</span> <span class="hps">-</span> <span class="hps">seguro</span> <span class="hps">pero agresivo</span>. <span class="hps">Él es conocido por</span> <span class="hps">repartiendo</span> <span class="hps">toneladas de</span> <span class="hps">daños</span>, teniendo <span class="hps">muy poco de su</span> <span class="hps">propia</span>. <span class="hps">En pocas palabras</span>, <span class="hps">él es uno de</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">mejores</span> <span class="hps">ADCs</span> <span class="hps">absolutos en</span> <span class="hps">China,</span> <span class="hps">una región conocida por</span> <span class="hps">la excelencia en</span> <span class="hps">la posición</span>. <span class="hps">Hay muy pocas cosas</span> <span class="hps">que pueden</span> <span class="hps">detener un</span> <span class="hps">namei</span> <span class="hps">bola de nieve</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>DanDy</strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Al igual</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span>, <span class="hps">Samsung</span> <span class="hps">Galaxy</span> <span class="hps">White</span> <span class="hps">pone mucha</span> <span class="hps">fe</span> <span class="hps">y se centran</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">su</span> <span class="hps">jungler</span>. <span class="hps">Dandy</span> <span class="hps">es la piedra angular</span> <span class="hps">para</span> <span class="hps">el equipo</span> <span class="hps">objetivo</span> <span class="hps">centrado en</span> <span class="hps">las blancas</span>, hacer llamadas <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">discusiones</span> <span class="hps">sus compañeros de equipo</span> <span class="hps">para estar en</span> <span class="hps">el lugar correcto en</span> <span class="hps">el momento adecuado</span>. <span class="hps">Es raro que</span> <span class="hps">un momento en el</span> <span class="hps">Dandy</span> <span clas