pan class="hps">temprano y con frecuencia</span>, <span class="hps">Clearlove</span> <span class="hps">es a menudo el</span> <span class="hps">uno</span> <span class="hps">a la cabeza.</span> <span class="hps">Sobresaliendo</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">la agresión</span> <span class="hps">desenfrenada</span> <span class="hps">en medio del juego</span>, <span class="hps">que es</span> <span class="hps">casi</span> <span class="hps">siempre el que</span> <span class="hps">dar el primer paso</span> <span class="hps">para poner fin a</span> <span class="hps">la fase</span> <span class="hps">de encarrilamiento</span>.\r\n\r\n<span class="hps">Que</span> <span class="hps">la agresión</span> <span class="hps">puede ser</span> <span class="hps">su caída</span>, sin embargo. <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">se pone detrás</span>, <span class="hps">el exceso de confianza</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">Clearlove</span> <span class="hps">puede</span> <span class="hps">-</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">será</span> <span class="hps">- enviándolos</span> <span class="hps">en una espiral de</span> <span class="hps">intentos</span> <span class="hps">fallidos</span> <span class="hps">de lucha</span>. <span class="hps">Su</span> <span class="hps">éxito o</span> <span class="hps">fracaso a menudo</span> <span class="hps">define</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">de</span>.</span>\r\n<strong>Touch</strong>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">No se sabe mucho</span> <span class="hps">acerca de Touch</span>. <span class="hps">Él</span> <span class="hps">se unió a</span> <span class="hps">Dark Passage</span> <span class="hps">muy tarde en</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">proceso de calificación</span> <span class="hps">para el Mundial</span>, <span class="hps">pero no obstante</span> <span class="hps">tenía</span> <span class="hps">demostraciones</span> <span class="hps">impresionantes</span>. <span class="hps">Sin embargo</span>, <span class="hps">como él</span> <span class="hps">va a ir</span> <span class="hps">en contra de</span> <span class="hps">Mata</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Fzzf</span>, <span class="hps">fácilmente</span> <span class="hps">dos de los</span> <span class="hps">mejores</span> <span class="hps">apoyos</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">el mundo</span>, que va a <span class="hps">más de</span> <span class="hps">tener</span> <span class="hps">las manos llenas</span>. <span class="hps">Si él</span> <span class="hps">va aún</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">los golpea</span> <span class="hps">podríamos estar en</span> <span class="hps">algún</span> <span class="hps">emocionante acción de</span> <span class="hps">malestar</span> <span class="hps">durante la</span> <span class="hps">Fase de grupos</span>.</span>\r\n<h3>Our prediction</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">La forma en</span> <span class="hps">que lo vemos</span>, <span class="hps">hay muy</span> <span class="hps">pocas posibilidades de que</span> <span class="hps">Dark Passage</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">AHQ</span> <span class="hps">hacen</span> <span class="hps">fuera de</span> <span class="hps">la fase de grupos</span>. <span class="hps">Salvo alguna</span> <span class="hps">grave</span> <span class="hps">lanza</span> <span class="hps">por</span> <span class="hps">tanto</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Blanco</span>, <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">Comodín</span> <span class="hps">Internacional y</span> <span class="hps">equipos</span> <span class="hps">del sudeste asiático</span> <span class="hps">son simplemente demasiado</span> <span class="hps">inconsistente para</span> <span class="hps">enfrentarse cara</span> <span class="hps">a cara con</span> <span class="hps">dos de los</span> <span class="hps">mejores equipos</span> <span class="hps">del Este</span> <span class="hps">tiene para ofrecer</span>.\r\n\r\n<span class="hps">AHQ</span> <span class="hps">tiene</span> <span class="hps">una cosa</span> <span class="hps">en su lado</span>: <span class="hps">un chip</span> <span class="hps">enorme en</span> <span class="hps">su</span> <span class="hps">hombro.</span> <span class="hps">Esta</span> <span class="hps">es la primera vez</span> <span class="hps">que han conseguido</span> <span class="hps">llegar al</span> <span class="hps">torneo de</span> <span class="hps">Campeonato del Mundo,</span> <span class="hps">y usted puede apostar</span> <span class="hps">westdoor</span> <span class="hps">estarán buscando</span> <span class="hps">para hacer una impresión</span>. <span class="hps">Incluso pueden</span> <span class="hps">coger</span> <span class="hps">tanto</span> <span class="hps">EDG</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Blanco</span> <span class="hps">en los días libres</span><span>, dándoles</span> <span class="hps">una oportunidad</span> <span class="hps">de sorprender al mundo</span>.</span>\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Dark Passage</span>, <span class="hps">por el contrario</span>, <span class="hps">va a tener</span> <span class="hps">un momento difícil</span> <span class="hps">de la misma.</span> <span class="hps">Tienen muy</span> <span class="hps">poca experiencia</span> <span class="hps">contra</span> <span class="hps">los mejores</span> <span class="hps">equipos del mundo</span>. <span class="hps">Si tienen</span> <span class="hps">algo especial</span> <span class="hps">en la manga</span> <span class="hps">de la escena</span> <span class="hps">turca</span>, <span class="hps">sin embargo, pueden</span> <span class="hps">manejar a tomar</span> <span class="hps">un juego</span> <span class="hps">fuera</span> <span class="hps">de uno de los</span> <span class="hps">otros</span> <span class="hps">equipos del grupo</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n1. <strong>Samsung Galaxy White</strong>\r\n\r\n2. <strong>Edward Gaming</strong>\r\n\r\n3. AHQ e-Sports Club\r\n\r\n4. Dark Passage\r\n\r\n<em> </em>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Breaking down Group A', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '75-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-12 17:26:57', '2014-09-12 17:26:57', '', 75, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=76', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
