(81, 1, '2014-09-12 17:40:11', '2014-09-12 17:40:11', '<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Caos controlado</span> <span class="hps">será el</span> <span class="hps">nombre del juego</span> <span class="hps">en el Grupo</span> <span class="hps">B.</span> <span class="hps">Con cuatro</span> <span class="hps">escuadrones</span> <span class="hps">que les encanta</span> <span class="hps">teamfight</span>, <span class="hps">juegos</span> <span class="hps">será</span> <span class="hps">sangrienta y</span> <span class="hps">personas morirán</span>. <span class="hps">Una gran cantidad</span>.\r\n\r\n<span class="hps">¿El</span> <span class="hps">resto del grupo</span> <span class="hps">será capaz de manejar</span> <span class="hps">la</span> <span class="hps">despiadada</span> <span class="hps">estrella</span> <span class="hps">Horn</span> <span class="hps">Royal</span> <span class="hps">Club?</span> <span class="hps">¿Puede</span> <span class="hps">TSM</span> <span class="hps">aprovechar su</span> <span class="hps">impulso</span> <span class="hps">desde</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">Playoffs</span> <span class="hps">de verano</span> <span class="hps">NA</span> <span class="hps">LCS</span>? <span class="hps">Prevalecerá</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">trabajo en equipo</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">SK</span> <span class="hps">Gaming</span>? <span class="hps">¿O el</span> <span class="hps">Assassins</span> <span class="hps">Taipei</span> <span class="hps">sorprender al mundo</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">una repetición</span> <span class="hps">de la temporada 2</span>? <span class="hps">He aquí cómo</span> <span class="hps">lo vemos.</span> </span>\r\n<h3>Teams</h3>\r\n<h4>Team SoloMid</h4>\r\n<img src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/TSM%20Champions3.jpg?itok=zgGgjRu3" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Top:</strong> Dyrus\r\n<strong>Jungle