(83, 1, '2014-09-12 17:41:14', '2014-09-12 17:41:14', '<span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Caos controlado</span> <span class="hps">será el</span> <span class="hps">nombre del juego</span> <span class="hps">en el Grupo</span> <span class="hps">B.</span> <span class="hps">Con cuatro</span> <span class="hps">escuadrones</span> <span class="hps">que les encanta</span> <span class="hps">teamfight</span>, <span class="hps">juegos</span> <span class="hps">será</span> <span class="hps">sangrienta y</span> <span class="hps">personas morirán</span>. <span class="hps">Una gran cantidad</span>.</span>\n\n<span class="hps">¿El</span> <span class="hps">resto del grupo</span> <span class="hps">será capaz de manejar</span> <span class="hps">la</span> <span class="hps">despiadada</span> <span class="hps">estrella</span> <span class="hps">Horn</span> <span class="hps">Royal</span> <span class="hps">Club?</span> <span class="hps">¿Puede</span> <span class="hps">TSM</span> <span class="hps">aprovechar su</span> <span class="hps">impulso</span> <span class="hps">desde</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">Playoffs</span> <span class="hps">de verano</span> <span class="hps">NA</span> <span class="hps">LCS</span>? <span class="hps">Prevalecerá</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">trabajo en equipo</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">SK</span> <span class="hps">Gaming</span>? <span class="hps">¿O el</span> <span class="hps">Assassins</span> <span class="hps">Taipei</span> <span class="hps">sorprender al mundo</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">una repetición</span> <span class="hps">de la temporada 2</span>? <span class="hps">He aquí cómo</span> <span class="hps">lo vemos.</span>\n<h3>Teams</h3>\n<h4>Team SoloMid</h4>\n<img src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/TSM%20Champions3.jpg?itok=zgGgjRu3" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Top:</strong> Dyrus\n<strong>Jungle:</strong> Amazing\n<strong>Mid:</strong> Bjergsen\n<strong>ADC:</strong> WildTurtle\n<strong>Support:</strong> Lustboy\n\n<span lang="es">\n<span class="hps">Los</span> <span class="hps">chicos están de vuelta</span> <span class="hps">en la ciudad.</span> <span class="hps">Después de tres</span> <span class="hps">divisiones</span> <span class="hps">de ver</span> <span class="hps">Cloud9</span> <span class="hps">tomar</span> <span class="hps">campeonato</span> <span class="hps">de América del Norte</span> <span class="hps">después</span> <span class="hps">del campeonato</span> <span class="hps">de América del Norte</span>, <span class="hps">TSM</span> <span class="hps">por fin ha</span> <span class="hps">recuperado su</span> <span class="hps">trono como los</span> <span class="hps">reyes de</span> <span class="hps">NA</span>.</span>\n\n<span class="hps">Sobre el papel</span>, <span class="hps">TSM</span> <span class="hps">es el paquete</span> <span class="hps">completo</span>. <span class="hps">Tienen</span> <span class="hps">dos</span> <span class="hps">de larga data</span> <span class="hps">veteranos</span> <span class="hps">NA</span> <span class="hps">LCS</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">Dyrus</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">WildTurtle</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">tres</span> <span class="hps">importaciones</span> <span class="hps">inmensamente</span> <span class="hps">talentosos</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">Lustboy</span>, Amazing, <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">Bjergsen</span>. <span class="hps">Ellos tienen</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">liderazgo y</span> <span class="hps">el talento para</span> <span class="hps">llegar lejos.</span> <span class="hps">Y</span> <span class="hps">a pesar de algunas</span> <span class="hps">luchas</span> <span class="hps">durante la temporada regular</span>, parece <span class="hps">como si estuvieran</span> <span class="hps">en ese tren</span> <span class="hps">del éxito</span> <span class="hps">después de caer</span> <span class="hps">Cloud9</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">Playoffs</span> <span class="hps">de verano</span> <span class="hps">NA</span> <span class="hps">LCS</span>.\n\n<span class="hps">Con el impulso</span> <span class="hps">de su</span> <span class="hps">gran victoria</span> <span class="hps">NA</span> <span class="hps">LCS</span> <span class="hps">en</span> <span class="hps">su</span> <span class="hps">espalda,</span> <span class="hps">TSM</span> <span class="hps">puede</span> <span class="hps">finalmente</span> <span class="hps">ser capaz de</span> <span class="hps">vivir de acuerdo con</span> <span class="hps">el potencial de</span> <span class="hps">su plantilla</span> <span class="hps">contiene</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">hacer una carrera en</span> <span class="hps">el Campeonato del Mundo</span>. <span class="hps">Sólo</span> <span class="hps">tienes que</span> <span class="hps">pasar por</span> <span class="hps">el Grupo B</span> <span class="hps">en primer lugar.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n<h4>Star Horn Royal Club</h4>\n<img src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Royal.jpg?itok=fdqmwalx" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Top:</strong> Cola\n<strong>Jungle:</strong> inSec\n<strong>Mid:</strong> Corn\n<strong>ADC:</strong> Uzi\n<strong>Support:</strong> Zero\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span class="hps">Si hay un</span> <span class="hps">equipo</span> <span class="hps">que ejemplifica</span> <span class="hps">el estilo chino</span> <span class="hps atn">hiper-</span>agresiva de <span class="hps">League of Legends</span>, <span class="hps">que es</span> <span class="hps">la estrella</span> <span class="hps">de Hornos</span> <span class="hps">Royal</span> <span class="hps">Club.</span> <span class="hps">Ellos</span> <span class="hps">nunca hacia abajo</span> <span class="hps">de una pelea</span>, <span class="hps">teniendo</span> <span class="hps">victorias en</span> <span class="hps">caóticas</span>, <span class="hps">baños de sangre</span> <span class="hps">bola de nieve</span>.\n\n<span class="hps">A pesar de su</span> <span class="hps">estilo</span> <span class="hps">decididamente</span> <span class="hps">china</span> <span class="hps">del juego</span>, <span class="hps">SHRC</span> <span class="hps">cuenta con un</span> <span class="hps">par de</span> <span class="hps">jugadores coreanos</span> <span class="hps">talentosos en</span> <span class="hps">jungler</span> <span class="hps">Insec</span> <span class="hps">y apoyo</span> <span class="hps">Zero</span>. <span class="hps">Afortunadamente</span> <span class="hps">para el equipo,</span> <span class="hps">el par</span> <span class="hps">son más que capaces</span> <span class="hps">de igualar</span> <span class="hps">la agresión</span> <span class="hps">del equipo</span> <span class="hps">-</span> <span class="hps">y algo más.</span> <span class="hps">Quizás como resultado</span> <span class="hps">de los problemas</span> <span class="hps">de la barrera linguística</span>, <span class="hps">Insec</span> <span class="hps">se conoció</span> <span class="hps">durante la temporada</span> <span class="hps">regular para irse</span> <span class="hps">demasiado</span> <span class="hps">duro detrás de</span> <span class="hps">las líneas enemigas</span> <span class="hps">sin</span> <span class="hps">sus compañeros de equipo</span> <span class="hps">para respaldarlo</span>. <span class="hps">Cuando</span> <span class="hps">SHRC</span> <span class="hps">pierde</span>, <span class="hps">su</span> <span class="hps">normalmente</span> <span class="hps">en la parte posterior</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">los</span> <span class="hps">problemas de comunicación</span>.\n\n<span class="hps">Y luego</span>, hay <span class="hps">Uzi</span>. <span class="hps">Una de</span> <span class="hps">la</span> <span class="hps">principal</span> <span class="hps">AD</span> <span class="hps">lleva en</span> <span class="hps">el mundo</span>, <span class="hps">es conocido</span> <span class="hps">por su habilidad para</span> <span class="hps">el buceo</span> <span class="hps">en solitario</span> <span class="hps">ganar</span> <span class="hps">teamfights</span>, <span class="hps">de cabeza en</span> <span class="hps">el peligro</span> <span class="hps">de hacer lo mejor</span> <span class="hps">para dejar</span> <span class="hps">a tantos enemigos</span> <span class="hps">como sea posible</span>. <span class="hps">A</span> <span class="hps">Uzi</span> <span class="hps">bola de nieve</span> <span class="hps">se convierte en un</span> <span class="hps">Royal Club</span> <span class="hps">muy peligroso</span>.\n<h4>Taipei Assassins</h4>\n<img src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/TPA.jpg?itok=svjJU327" alt="" />\n\n<strong>Top:</strong> Achie\n<strong>Jungle:</strong> Winds\n<strong>Mid:</strong> Morning\n<strong>ADC:</strong> BeBe\n<strong>Support:</strong> Jay\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span class="hps">Nunca cuente</span> <span class="hps">el</span> <span class="hps">Assassins</span> <span class="hps">Taipei</span>. <span class="hps">Camino de regreso</span> <span class="hps">en el torneo</span> <span class="hps">World Championship</span> <span class="hps">Season</span> <span class="hps">2</span>, <span class="hps">que salió</span> <span class="hps">de la nada para</span> <span class="hps">sorprender al</span> <span class="hps">escenario internacional</span> <span class="hps">y marcharse</span> <span class="hps">con</span> <span class="hps">la Copa del</span> <span class="hps">invocador</span>.\n\n<span class="hps">Desde entonces</span>, sin embargo, el rostro de <span class="hps">TPA</span> <span class="hps">ha sido objeto de</span> <span class="hps">una revisión</span> <span class="hps">casi completa</span>. <span class="hps">Todos menos</