(169, 1, '2014-09-29 11:27:34', '2014-09-29 11:27:34', '<div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">\r\n<div class="field-items">\r\n<div class="field-item even">\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">1. Meteos- 57.9% (963 Votos)</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/Meteos%20%282%20of%207%29_0.jpg?itok=U58sM7jU" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>LCS Elise Estadisticas:</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Jugados</em>: 5</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Ganados</em>: 3</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Ratio</em>: 60%</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em> KDA:</em> 6.1</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> apply red buff with an auto attack before going for a stun to make it easier to hit</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Will Hartman (@meteoslol) <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol/statuses/504463837987614720"><span style="color: #000000;">August 27, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Si bien hay</span> <span class="hps">campeones</span> <span class="hps">que</span> <span class="hps">pueden tener éxito</span> <span class="hps">sin ellos</span>, <span class="hps">una especie de</span> <span class="hps">brecha de</span> <span class="hps">cerca</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">hace que</span> <span class="hps">la presión</span> <span class="hps">del juego</span> <span class="hps">temprano y</span> <span class="hps">ganks</span> <span class="hps">mucho más fácil</span>. <span class="hps">Disparos</span> <span class="hps">de habilidad</span> <span class="hps">que falte en un</span> <span class="hps">ataque en masa</span> <span class="hps">pueden</span> <span class="hps">terminar perdiendo</span> <span class="hps">un valioso tiempo de</span> <span class="hps">selva</span> <span class="hps">claro.</span> <span class="hps">Capullo</span> <span class="hps">de Elise</span> <span class="hps">puede ser muy</span> <span class="hps">difícil de golpear</span> <span class="hps">si el</span> <span class="hps">compañero de equipo</span> <span class="hps">que estés</span> <span class="hps">ganking</span> <span class="hps">para</span> <span class="hps">no tiene</span> <span class="hps">algún tipo de</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">fiable</span>, <span class="hps">así que trate de</span> <span class="hps">ataque</span> <span class="hps">automático con</span> <span class="hps">piel de ante</span> <span class="hps">de color rojo</span> <span class="hps">para que sea un</span> <span class="hps">poco más fácil</span> <span class="hps">para usted</span>.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">2. Shook - 15.8% (262 Votos)</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/shookface.jpg?itok=KDjDsPXf" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></span></a> <strong>LCS Elise Estadisticas:</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Jugados</em>:9</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Ganados</em>: 7</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Ratio</em>: 77.8%</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>KDA</em>: 2.9</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<center></center>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">  </span>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> When ganking just apply redbuff and use your damaging abbilities, hold on to your cocoon until they flash. — Shook (@ShookLoL) <a href="https://twitter.com/ShookLoL/statuses/504778852149649408"><span style="color: #000000;">August 27, 2014</span></a></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<div id="gt-res-content" class="almost_half_cell">\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"><span id="result_box" lang="es" style="color: #000000;"><span class="hps">Shook</span> <span class="hps">refuerza</span> <span class="hps">lo</span> <span class="hps">Meteos</span> <span class="hps">nos dijo</span>, <span class="hps">porque</span> <span class="hps">incluso los profesionales</span> <span class="hps">saben que es</span> <span class="hps">fácil pasar por alto</span> <span class="hps">un capullo</span>. <span class="hps">La</span> <span class="hps">piel de ante</span> <span class="hps">rojo</span> <span class="hps">lento</span> <span class="hps">también</span> <span class="hps">hará que sea</span> <span class="hps">más fácil para sus</span> <span class="hps">Laners</span> <span class="hps">para golpear a</span> <span class="hps">cualquier</span> <span class="hps">cc</span> <span class="hps">​​que tienen,</span> <span class="hps">como un gancho</span> <span class="hps">Thresh</span> <span class="hps">o</span> <span class="hps">una burbuja de</span> <span class="hps">Nami</span>.</span></div>\r\n<div dir="ltr" style="zoom: 1;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Tips de la comunidad</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol"><span style="color: #000000;">@meteoslol</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> cocoon flash is a nice way to hit an unexpected stun. channel your cocoon and then cancel the animation with flash</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— I Will Dominate (@CrsDominate) <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate/statuses/504469712701779968"><span style="color: #000000;">August 27, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script><span id="result_box" lang="es"><span class="hps">Había un poco de</span> <span class="hps">debate</span> <span class="hps">en Twitter</span> <span class="hps">en torno a</span> <span class="hps">éste</span>, así que <span class="hps">probé</span> <span class="hps">yo mismo</span> <span class="hps">sólo para estar seguro</span> <span class="hps">(no es que</span> <span class="hps">no confíe en ti</span>, <span class="hps">Dom)</span>. <span class="hps">Uso del flash</span> <span class="hps">inmediatamente</span> <span class="hps">después de la fundición</span> <span class="hps">capullo</span> <span class="hps">cancela</span> <span class="hps">la animación</span> <span class="hps">canalización</span> <span class="hps">y</span> <span class="hps">arroja</span> <span class="hps">el capullo</span> <span class="hps">al instante</span> <span class="hps">de la</span> <span class="hps">ubicación final</span> <span class="hps">del</span> <span class="hps">flash</span>. <span class="hps">Esto significa</span> <span class="hps">menos tiempo</span> <span class="hps">al enemigo para</span> <span class="hps">reaccionar y</span> <span class="hps">una mayor probabilidad de</span> <span class="hps">golpear</span>.</span></span>\r\n<center></center>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">  </span>\r\n\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> Starting off tower dives is great on Elise. She can tank 2-3 shots and then repel in order to reset tower Aggro. — TomsGG (@SomePlatDude) <a href="https://twitter.com/SomePlatDude/statuses/504877341772742656"><span style="color: #000000;">August 28, 2014</span></a></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es" style="color: #000000;"><span class="hps">Mientras</span> <span class="hps">torretas</span> <span class="hps">de buceo</span> <span class="hps">puede ser peligroso</span>, especialmente <span class="hps">al principio del juego</span>, es <span class="hps">también</span> <span class="hps">una gran manera de</span> <span class="hps">bola de nieve</span> <span class="hps">sus</span> <span class="hps">carriles</span>. <span class="hps">Como</span> <span class="hps">SomePlatDude</span> <span class="hps">señala</span>, <span class="hps">Elise</span> <span class="hps">es muy bueno para</span> <span class="hps">iniciar</span> <span class="hps">ya que ella</span> <span class="hps">lo</span> <span class="hps">puede</span> <span class="hps">conseguir fácilmente</span> <span class="hps">fuera de rango</span> <span class="hps">aggro</span> <span class="hps">torre.</span></span>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">  </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/CrsDominate"><span style="color: #000000;">@CrsDominate</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/meteoslol"><span style="color: #000000;">@meteoslol</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> Using your spider form Q to close in distance when chasing through a creep wave. Small but noticable</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Ram Djemal (@BrokenshardEUW) <a href="https://twitter.com/BrokenshardEUW/statuses/504472221294014464"><span style="color: #000000;">August 27, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" type="mce-text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span id="result_box" lang="es" style="color: #000000;"><span class="hps">Aunque estoy</span> <span class="hps">seguro de que ninguno</span> <span class="hps">de</span> <span class="hps">nosotros ha</span> <span class="hps">perdido</span> <span class="hps">aturdimiento</span> <span class="hps">de Elise</span>, <span class="hps">Brokenshard</span> <span class="hps">ofrece</span> <span class="hps">un gran consejo</span> <span class="hps">para atacar a los</span> <span class="hps">enemigos</span>. <span class="hps">Si</span> <span class="hps">usted tiene</span> <span class="hps">suficientes</span> <span class="hps">dedos rápidos</span>, <span class="hps">también puede utilizar</span> <span class="hps">este truco</span> <span class="hps">como una manera de</span> <span class="hps">ponerse en posición</span> <span class="hps">para</span> <span class="hps">una mejor oportunidad de</span> <span class="hps">conseguir el</span> <span class="hps">aturdimiento</span> <span class="hps">en el primer lugar</span>.</span>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Elise ', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '30-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-29 11:27:34', '2014-09-29 11:27:34', '', 30, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=169', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(170, 1, '2014-09-29 11:27:51', '2014-09-29 11:27:51', '<h3><span style="color: #000000;">1. ZionSpartan - 72.8% (843 Votes)</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/811aea3286.jpg?itok=SbVzO5s1"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/811aea3286.jpg?itok=SbVzO5s1" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>LCS Jax Stats:</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Played</em>: 6</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Won</em>: 4</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Win Rate</em>: 66.7%</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Average KDA:</em> 2.7</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<pre id="line1"><span style="color: #000000;"> </span></pre>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas"><span style="color: #000000;">@CrsQuas</span></a> When it comes to splitpushing, never underestimate your ability to pressure the turret while ahead 1/2</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507393034355765248"><span style="color: #000000;">September 4, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n<center></center>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas"><span style="color: #000000;">@CrsQuas</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> You can always go for potshots on towers with jax when you are ahead, especially with a trinity force! :) — Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507393189377245184"><span style="color: #000000;">September 4, 2014</span></a></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Today we learned that if you ask ZionSpartan about one of his favorite champions, you get three tips for the price of one. Jax is a notoriously strong split pusher thanks to some help from a stacking attack speed passive. Everyone knows that turrets are week to lamp posts. Zion is suggesting that if you''ve got a lot of damage and are ahead in lane, don''t be afraid to poke the tower.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas"><span style="color: #000000;">@CrsQuas</span></a> Also, never underestimate the ability to initiate a teamfight by flash counterstriking into the enemy team!</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Darshan Upadhyaya (@ZionSpartan) <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan/status/507395748666015745"><span style="color: #000000;">September 4, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>And there''s the tip we really wanted. This is the Jax player dream: Flash-Leap Striking onto the enemy ADC and getting off that three man stun while your team (hopefully) follows up behind you. Bear in mind that you <em>have to</em> have good communication with your team or you''ll be a lonely Jax behind enemy lines. If you''re all on the same page, though, this is a really great initiate especially if your team can pile on the cc.</span>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">2. Quas - 12.3% (142 Votes)</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/78e19d419e.jpg?itok=knpUFC_e"><span style="color: #000000;"><img class="aligncenter" src="http://na.lolesports.com/sites/default/files/styles/article_image/public/78e19d419e.jpg?itok=knpUFC_e" alt="" width="700" height="315" /></span></a></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>LCS Jax Stats:</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Played</em>:6</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Games Won</em>: 2</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Win Rate</em>: 33.3%</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="color: #000000;"><em>Average KDA</em>: 1.6</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<center></center>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none">\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan"><span style="color: #000000;">@ZionSpartan</span></a> when it comes to lategame, make sure you save your E to protect yourself from the ADC rather than stun</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Diego Ruiz (@CrsQuas) <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas/status/507390989104054272"><span style="color: #000000;">September 4, 2014</span></a></span>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Essentially the opposite of Zion''s last tip, Quas''s recommendation is for the more even-keeled lover of Jax. While his E is a great way to initiate a teamfight, it also means that you''ll be completely vulnerable after you use it. If you don''t have a ton of armor, saving the invulnerability can be a safer way to play it...but where''s the fun in that?</span>\r\n<h3><span style="color: #000000;">Community Tips</span></h3>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" lang="en" xml:lang="en" data-conversation="none"><span style="color: #000000;"><a href="https://twitter.com/RiotKatana"><span style="color: #000000;">@RiotKatana</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/lolesports"><span style="color: #000000;">@lolesports</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/ZionSpartan"><span style="color: #000000;">@ZionSpartan</span></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CrsQuas"><span style="color: #000000;">@CrsQuas</span></a> the W is an auto attack reset. so you should use it immediately after an autoattack</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">— Cloudwalker/Angwar (@MalteMittelhaus) <a href="https://twitter.com/MalteMittelhaus/status/507169816218984448"><span style="color: #000000;">September 3, 2014</span></a></span></blockquote>\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Auto attack resets are an important part of being able to trade effectively. The extra burst of damage can easily be the difference between life and death, especially in the lonely island of top lane. Use your W immediately after auto attacking for a surprising burst of damage.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"> </span>', 'LCS Pro Tips: Jax', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-29 11:27:51', '2014-09-29 11:27:51', '', 1, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=170', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
